com.cognifide.qa.bb.logging.reporter

Class AbstractReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cognifide.qa.bb.logging.reporter.AbstractReporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Reporter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HtmlReporter, JsonReporter, SimpleReporter

    public abstract class AbstractReporter
extends Object
implements Reporter
    Base class for all reporters. Part of Visitor pattern implementation. Each TestReportElement should have a corresponding method in this class.
    The method that triggers generation of the report file is generateReport().
